sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor C as Customer
    participant APP as Customer App
    participant PAY as Payment Flow
    participant GW as Payment Gateway
    participant WH as Gateway Webhook
    participant API as Payment Controller
    participant CB as Cashback Earn Service
    participant CFG as Cashback Service
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant LEDGER as Cashback Ledger

    C->>APP: Confirm payment
    APP->>PAY: POST payments
    PAY->>GW: Create payment intent
    GW-->>PAY: paymentURL
    PAY-->>APP: paymentURL
    APP->>GW: Redirect through 3DS or wallet
    GW-->>WH: Webhook payment status Successful
    WH->>API: Handle paid webhook
    API->>API: Update payment status and paid at
    API->>API: Update order status to paid

    API->>CB: On payment paid
    CB->>CFG: Get restaurant config
    CFG-->>CB: Config or null

    alt No config or program inactive
        CB-->>API: Skip - no cashback program
    else Program active
        CB->>CB: Compute eligible amount from order total
        Note right of CB: VastPay today uses order total
        Note right of CB: VastMenu later subtracts tips

        alt Below minimum invoice amount
            CB-->>API: Skip - below threshold
        else Amount is eligible
            CB->>DB: Find enrollment by phone or user
            alt No enrollment
                Note over CB: If mandatory at checkout the customer was already blocked
                Note over CB: Otherwise silently skip
                CB-->>API: Skip - not enrolled
            else Has enrollment
                DB-->>CB: Enrollment row

                CB->>CB: Compute raw cashback
                CB->>CB: Apply per transaction cap
                CB->>CB: Compute vast fee on eligible amount
                CB->>CB: Compute available at and expires at

                CB->>DB: BEGIN
                CB->>DB: INSERT cashback lot
                DB-->>CB: Lot id

                alt Available immediately
                    CB->>DB: Increment available amount and lifetime earned
                else Holding period applies
                    CB->>DB: Increment pending amount and lifetime earned
                end

                CB->>LEDGER: INSERT earn event with balances and ids
                CB->>DB: COMMIT

                CB-->>API: Lot earned
                API-->>APP: Success with cashback earned
                APP-->>C: You earned cashback
            end
        end
    end

    Note over LEDGER: Hourly maturation cron promotes pending into available
    Note over LEDGER: Nightly expiration cron flips lots to expired
